features: SYMMETRICAL SHAPE: No “right side up” silicone pacifier for babies are fuss-free and won’t need to be adjusted to sit properly in baby’s mouth and fits perfectly under nose for easy breathing.
SILICONE NIPPLE: The BPA-free silicone boy and girl pacifier has the signature MAM design, with silky SkinSoft material and a symmetrical shape that's ideal for jaw and teeth development.
SELF - STERILIZING CASE: Add water and pop into the microwave to sterilize MAM silicone pacifiers 0-6 months in just 3 minutes and store in case for at home and travel to protect the pacifiers.
VENTILATED & COMFORTABLE SHIELD: These cute pacifiers for babies have a curved sterilizing shield with openings to keep baby comfortable, prevent moisture build-up, and allow baby’s skin to breathe.

HIGH QUALITY: Approved by 94% of babies*, our 100% BPA & BPS free silicone pacifiers meet or exceed US safety standards and are extremely durable while being soft and flexible for your baby's comfort.
body.description: The MAM Start Matte Newborn Pacifier was developed by leading pediatric dentists and psychologists to provide maximum comfort and style for newborn babies 0-6 months of age.* MAM silicone girl pacifier feature an innovative nipple designed to promote healthy oral development so you can soothe your toddler with confidence. Our orthodontic pacifiers for breastfed babies have a built-in air channel that naturally flattens and extends when sucked, mimicking a human nipple during breastfeeding. Plus, all of MAM's breastfeed pacifier nipples feature life-like, SkinSoft textured silicone. These pacifiers for baby feature a symmetrical nipple that fits perfectly in baby's mouth at any angle. With multiple baby boy pacifier and girl pacifiers shapes and shield sizes to pick from, MAM nipples are easily accepted by babies of all ages, with 94% nipple acceptance among babies tested.** Pacifiers kept in the closed self-sterilizing case will remain clean for up to 48 hours: Fill pacifier sterilizing case with water and place in the case with the nipple facing down. Follow pacifier package instructions for microwave setting. Cool completely before use. *Developed with the International Children's Medical Research Society. ***Market research 2010-2020, tested with 1,572 babies

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These were recommended to us by some friends before we had our little one and these pacifiers have consistently delivered. They've made our parenting journey smoother and more enjoyable. They have helped calm our babe. If you have a breastfed baby who's particular about pacifiers like my little one, I highly recommend giving these a try. They offer the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. We've purchased them multiple times and will continue to do so without hesitation. A must-have for any new parent!Breastfed Baby's Best Friend (5/5): Our baby, who is exclusively breastfed, can be quite particular about pacifiers. However, the MAM Original Start Matte pacifiers have won our baby's heart. They mimic the shape and feel of a mother's breast, making the transition between breastfeeding and pacifier seamless. Our little one took to them instantly and found comfort and satisfaction in these pacifiers. This was great because our little one rejected many other pacifiersSterilization on the Go (5/5): One of the standout features of these pacifiers is the convenient sterilization case they come with. Being able to quickly sterilize the pacifiers in the case is a game-changer, especially when we're on the move. It provides peace of mind knowing that our baby's pacifier is always clean and safe.Durable and Easy to Clean (5/5): These pacifiers are not only well-designed but also durable. They withstand frequent use and washing without showing signs of wear and tear. The materials used are easy to clean and maintain, which is a big plus for busy parents.Stylish and Matte Finish (5/5): The matte finish on these pacifiers adds a stylish touch. It's not only visually appealing but also provides a secure grip for our baby. The design is simple and elegant, which we appreciate. We also match our pacifier to our baby's outfits which looks so cute lol
